dct_description_sm: Map of Cranbury Township in Middlesex County, N.J. showing the border with Mercer County. Names of home and property owners are listed and a section of the Camden and Amboy Rail Road is included. Inset of Plainsboro P.O. streets and homes. Plate 30 of a multi page publication. Accompanying text on another page dates the map to no earlier than 1875.
